videos.headline: Pearl discusses heartfelt reaction to Auburn's SEC title
videos.description: The Tigers' Bruce Pearl gets emotional while explaining the lessons learned from his father that he now shares with his players and why this season's success means so much.

videos.headline: Broome says Auburn made statement with SEC title
videos.description: After leading the way with 19 points and 11 rebounds in an 86-67 win over Florida, Johnni Broome insists the Tigers are not done winning.
